lead_paragraph: Bradley Wright-Phillips scored two of New York's three goals in a 10-minute span and the Red Bulls rallied to beat Orlando City 3-2 on Sunday night to snap a four-game losing streak.

headline.print_headline: Bradley Wright-Phillips Leads Red Bulls Past Orlando City
